you don't have arch-type and class AA abilities, <br>
you aren't in a raiding guild....but you know the abilities and limitations of bards that have and do all of the above?&quot;<br>
<br>
The mechanics of EQ are not overly complex.<br>
Do not kid yourself.<br>
This is a TIME expenditure game, accumulating resources and learning then coordinating to apply those resources to defeat encounters, NOT a game of skill.<br>
The AI is NOT complex.<br>
And, MOST players do not even figure out the solution for scenarios for themselves but instead follow instructions/guides from others in how to do it.<br>
<br>
Doing extensive research, reading articles, posting questions, and using player made tools allows for a tremendous amount of understanding... even prior to actual in-game experience.<br>
Which is why I have the items I have at my level.<br>
That being said:<br>
60th slow: slows at a lower percent than the 51 slow, lasts a minutre, has a dot component.<br>
Rondo: has a stackable DS component, a smaller, non-stackable haste than many other bard songs, and str/atk adjustment.<br>
Warcry: 25% stackable haste, lasts 21 seconds<br>
60th level mana drain: 13 second recast, high mana drain, great song MOST bards will NEVER see this song<br>
bard AA: what magic rabbit you gonna pull out of this hat?<br>
What is your point?<br>
<br>
NO I do not have extensive raid experience, and I do chalk my comments on that area up to feedback from others.<br>
From responses they do not seem to be that out if line.<br>
<br>
&quot;I am not going to debate this stuff with you, because you are not working from a position of first-hand knowledge.&quot;<br>
&quot;I never chant kite, swarm kite, or charm kite&quot;<br>
<br>
You do not use bards in a manner consistent with the majority of bards out there, by your own logic (not mine) you should not comment on the playability of bards outside of uber guild raids and uber equiped bard soloing/group tactics. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulammfallaway.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lamm Fallaway</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/1/02 4:40:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=24490.topic&index=58>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bard issues</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  You want to compare Bards to Wizards, and then cry that they can't nuke as well? Give me a break. Can wizards melee? Can they run at super speed? Can they charm? No, stfu, thanks.<br>
